<p><i>Our Band Is Called…</i> is a Rock 'n' Roll band name generator implementing <a href="http://dubiousquality.blogspot.com/2008/01/rock-band-99.html">Bill Harris' algorithm</a>:</p>
<p>Your band is named after <a href="<%= @band_name_url %>">a random Wikipedia page</a>.</p>
<p>Your album comes from the last four words of <a href="<%= @album_name_url %>">a random quote</a>.</p>
<p>Your album cover is the third picture on <a href="<%= @album_cover_url %>">Flick's interesting pictures</a>.</p>
<p>Click on your album cover or refresh to generate a new band.</p>
